Mu [[Rwanda]] hatangijwe uburyo bwo kubungabunga ibidukikije haterwa [[Igiti|ibiti]] by 'imigano,  imigano miliyoni 3 imaze guterwa ku nkengero z’imigezi n’ibiyaga, ku buso bwa Hegitari 2,129 , muduce dutandukanye tw'igihugu harimo umwihariko mu nkengero z'imigezi , [[Ibiyaga Bigari|ibiyaga]], ibyuzi  harimo umugezi wa [[Umugezi wa Nyabarongo|Nyabarongo]],  n’Akanyaru,mu biyaga nki icya bugesera , ruhondo ,[[Ikiyaga cya Muhazi|muhazi]] na handi , no munkengero ya [[Pariki y’Igihugu y’Ibirunga|pariki y'ibirunga]]<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ibidukikije/ibungabunga/Musanze-Imigano-yitaweho-yaba-igisubizo-ku-kwangiza-amashyamba</ref><ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ibidukikije/ibungabunga/article/mu-rwanda-hagiye-kubakwa-uruganda-rutunganya-ibikoresho-mu-migano</ref> .

== Akamaro k'igiti cy'umugano ==
Imigano ni biti byiza  mu kubungabunga ibidukikije no mu buzima bwa burimunsi bwa muntu kuko havamo ibikoresho bitandukanye .

Imwe mu mimaro y'imigano<ref>https://www.igihe.com/ibidukikije/article/hatangijwe-umushinga-wo-gutera-imigano-izajya-itunganywa-ikabyazwamo-ibindi</ref> :

* Ibungabunga urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima ni ibimera.
* Imigano ifata ubutaka mu kurwanya isuri
* Imigano ni ibiti bigira uruhare mu kurwanya imihindagurikire y'ikirere n'ibiza .

* Imigano ikorwamo bimwe mubikoresho byifashishwa na muntu ;urugero nk'intebe ,ameza, imitako nibindi<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ibidukikije/ibungabunga/article/mu-rwanda-hagiye-kubakwa-uruganda-rutunganya-ibikoresho-mu-migano</ref>....

* Imigano ikoreshwa mu kubaka amazu <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ibidukikije/ibungabunga/article/menya-byinshi-ku-kamaro-k-imigano-inaribwa</ref>



== Umwihariko udasanzwe ku giti cy'umugano ==
[[Dosiye:Imigano ku mazi.jpg|thumb|Zimwe mu nkengero z'imigezi hateweho  ibiti by'imigano.]]
Mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] nyuma yo kubyaza inyungu igiti cy'umugano noneho hagiye guterwa imigano iribwa nk'ibiryo ,nki ibintu bitari bimenyerewe ku bazi umugano banawubyaza inyungu .Abaryi bimigano mu bindi bihugu bavugako havamo ibiribwa bitandukanye biryoha <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ibidukikije/ibungabunga/article/menya-byinshi-ku-kamaro-k-imigano-inaribwa</ref>.

